chukua zaidi yangu, nipe zaidi yako, Roho Mtakatifu.

0:56:38.140,0:56:40.180
Asante, mpigie makofi.

0:56:40.180,0:56:42.300
Umesikia?

0:56:42.300,0:56:48.740
Hizi bangili za kukuza imani ilipotolewa, maneno ya kutumia yalifuata - "chukua zaidi yangu, nipe zaidi yako".

0:56:48.740,0:56:58.500
Nimewapa mengine leo: "Niguse katika Rehema zako...

0:56:58.500,0:57:08.020
Niguse katika fadhili zako, niguse katika rehema yako...

0:57:08.020,0:57:09.700
chukua zaidi yangu, nipe zaidi yako".

0:57:09.700,0:57:13.180
Hata ninapokuombea, endelea kufanya hiyo tafakari,

0:57:13.180,0:57:17.780
"Niguse katika fadhili zako, niguse katika Rehema zako".

0:57:17.780,0:57:20.380
Asante, dada.

0:57:20.380,0:57:21.980
Mwingine tena?

0:57:21.980,0:57:24.380
Sawa, mpe ndugu hapo.

0:57:24.380,0:57:27.840
Emmanuel.

0:57:27.840,0:57:31.880
Ni mara yangu ya kwanza kufika SCOAN.

0:57:31.880,0:57:37.420
Ninasikiliza Emmanuel TV muda wote.

0:57:37.420,0:57:39.960
Emmanuel TV imebadilisha maisha yangu.

0:57:39.960,0:57:44.820
sikuwahi kusoma Biblia awali, hadi nilipoanza kutazama Emmanuel TV.

0:57:44.820,0:57:50.540
Nilipoanza kutazama Emmanuel TV, nilimuona Mtumishi wa Mungu akihubiri,

0:57:50.540,0:57:58.280
akitoa ushauri kwamba tutafakari - "Nipe zaidi yako, Mungu, chukua zaidi yangu".

0:57:58.280,0:58:00.860
Nilizingatia hiyo tahadhari.

0:58:00.860,0:58:05.320
Mimi ni mfamasia; nina famasi yangu.

0:58:05.320,0:58:10.240
Ninatoa ushauri kwa wagonjwa, ninaonana nao kila siku.

0:58:10.240,0:58:16.980
Kuna tukio moja, nilikuwa ofisini kwangu nikihudumia wagonjwa.

0:58:16.980,0:58:21.560
na nilikuwa nimezingatia ushauri wa "Nipe zaidi yako, chukua zaidi yangu".

0:58:21.560,0:58:23.500
Siku hiyo nilikuwa nafanya hivyo.

0:58:23.500,0:58:31.380
Nilikuwa nahudumia mgonjwa nikitafakari, "Nipe zaidi yako, chukua zaidi yangu".

0:58:31.380,0:58:33.160
tazama!

0:58:33.160,0:58:36.860
Mama na binti yake.

0:58:36.860,0:58:40.740
baada ya mama kulalamika, binti akafuatia.

0:58:40.740,0:58:51.320
nilipokuwa nikiongea, nilikuwa natafakari, "Nipe zaidi yako, chukua zaidi yangu, Bwana..."

0:58:51.320,0:58:58.040
halafu nikamuuliza binti, "hujambo? jina lako nani?"

0:58:58.040,0:58:59.480
Nikamwambia, "Nipe mkono".

0:58:59.480,0:59:06.900
Niliposhika mkono wa huyu binti, akasema, "niache! unanifahamu

0:59:06.900,0:59:11.280
Unanijua mimi ni nani? unaniona mdogo. Mimi ni mwanamke mkubwa".

0:59:11.280,0:59:15.800
Mama yake, alikuwa amekaa karibu naye, hakuja cho chote.

0:59:15.800,0:59:17.460
Kusema kweli, Nilipata mshtuko.

0:59:17.460,0:59:23.280
Nilikuwa naangalia, na nikasema, "Utukufu ni wake Mungu. Mungu wa Nabii TB Joshua amenipeleka mpaka eneo hili.

0:59:23.280,0:59:26.320
Ninataka kwenda zaidi kwa undani kwenye eneo jingine."

0:59:26.320,0:59:29.640
Mmesikia hiyo?

0:59:29.640,0:59:34.300
Mnakumbuka nilicho wambia, kwamba maombi mliyozoea kuomba -

0:59:34.300,0:59:38.760
kwa muda wote, mmekuwa mkipoteza muda wenu.

0:59:38.760,0:59:46.600
Maombi ni ya moyo, lakini maombi yenu ni ya mdomo.

0:59:46.600,0:59:47.900
Mnapoteza muda wenu.

0:59:47.900,0:59:55.280
Kila mara ninapoona watu wakisema, "katika Jina la Yesu...", huwa nasema, "Ooo - mnakaribisha mashambulizi".

0:59:55.280,1:00:02.440
mtajirekebisha sasa na kuanza tafakari - hayo ndio maombi mnayohitaji kwa sasa.

1:00:02.440,1:00:06.540
mlivyo kaa, nini kinaendelea kwenye mioyo yenu?

1:00:06.540,1:00:09.900
muulize jirani yako, "Nini kinaendelea katika moyo wako?

1:00:09.900,1:00:12.800
Umedhibiti moyo wako?

1:00:12.800,1:00:16.040
unausimamia?

1:00:16.040,1:00:24.620
ongea mwenyewe katika Zaburi, tenzi za Rohoni na nyimbo za kiroho.

1:00:24.620,1:00:29.020
Imba mziki katika moyo wako."

1:00:29.020,1:00:33.920
Huduma ya SCOAN ya Jumapili

1:00:33.920,1:00:36.420
Unaona kinachotokea sasa.

1:00:36.420,1:00:41.880
Alikuwa anatafakari katika moyo wake, hakuna aliyejua anachosema katika moyo wake,

1:00:41.880,1:00:51.220
lakini kitendo cha kunyoosha mkono kwa mtoto, "niache! mimi ni hiki" - alianza kukiri.

1:00:51.220,1:00:54.840
unaendelea kujidanganya - unasema unaomba.

1:00:54.840,1:00:57.400
Wale wasiopaswa kukuombea wanakuombea;

1:00:57.400,1:01:01.540
wewe ni mzuri zaidi yao lakini wanakuombea.

1:01:01.540,1:01:05.600
Maombi yamekuwa utamaduni, desturi.

1:01:05.600,1:01:13.200
Maombi si desturi, yanatakiwa kuwa kwa kadiri ilivyo kwa mapenzi ya Mungu.

1:01:13.200,1:01:16.500
Unaamka asubuhi, unasema, "tuombe".

1:01:16.500,1:01:23.440
Badala ya kuishauri kwanza familia yako kwanza, "Halo. Asubuhi njema. Nini kimetokea?

1:01:23.440,1:01:28.000
Nini kilitokea jana? Niliwasahihisha jana. nilikwambia usifanya hiki.

1:01:28.000,1:01:35.140
Natumaini umejifunza kutokana na hilo. SAWA. Nini kinaendelea shuleni. tafadhali, njoo.

1:01:35.140,1:01:40.100
Unavyoonekana sio sawa, unalea uovu. tafadhali, kuwa mwangalifu kama Mkristo.

1:01:40.100,1:01:42.280
Una maumivu yo yote? Nini kinakutia wasiwasi?"

1:01:42.280,1:01:45.560
Huu ni ushauri unahitaji kuutoa kwa familia yako.

1:01:45.560,1:01:52.060
Baada ya unasihi huo utawaambia kuhusu Yesu, Roho Mtakatifu ninayemuongelea sasa.

1:01:52.060,1:01:58.400
"Hiki ndicho Biblia inachosema na Nabii TB Joshua alichotaja pia Jumapili iliyopita -

1:01:58.400,1:02:03.800
Inabidi uongee peke yako ndani ya moyo wako; ongea peke yako – hayo ndiyo maombi makubwa."

1:02:03.800,1:02:07.160
Maombi mengine yote ni madogo.

1:02:07.160,1:02:13.260
Maombi makubwa ni kuongea ndani ya moyo wako, dhibiti moyo wako,

1:02:13.260,1:02:21.660
Ongea peke yako kwa Zaburi, tenzi za Rohoni, imba mziki unapotembea, unapolala, muda wote.

1:02:21.660,1:02:29.720
Hayo ndiyo maombi makubwa yanayomshinda adui, yatakayokusaidia, yatakayokulinda.

1:02:29.720,1:02:30.940
Hayo ndio maombi!

1:02:30.940,1:02:48.620
Yale mnayoomba siku hizi ya kuamka na kusema, "katika Jina la Yesu, nakukemea!" - nani unayeongea?

1:02:48.620,1:02:50.760
Unapoteza muda.

1:02:50.760,1:02:53.240
Mmeona mengi juu ya maombi haya.

1:02:53.240,1:02:58.700
Unaweza kuona kwamba hakuna...

1:02:58.700,1:03:03.080
Asante, ndugu. mpigie makofi.

1:03:03.080,1:03:06.920
Huduma ya SCOAN ya Jumapili

1:03:06.920,1:03:09.640
Maombi mazuri ni yapi kwa Mungu?

1:03:09.640,1:03:10.860
Ye yote unayeweza?

1:03:10.860,1:03:12.380
Mpe ndugu pale.

1:03:12.380,1:03:17.180
Maombi bora sana.

1:03:17.180,1:03:19.260
Emmanuel.

1:03:19.260,1:03:23.080
Maombi bora kabisa ni maombi yanayotoka moyoni.

1:03:23.080,1:03:25.040
Ni jinsi gani maombi yanaweza kutoka moyoni?

1:03:25.040,1:03:30.760
Unapokuwa unatafakari Neno la Mungu moyoni, na moyo wako umeungana na Mungu,

1:03:30.760,1:03:34.580
Hayo ndiyo maombi bora daima.

1:03:34.580,1:03:35.880
Nina mfano.

1:03:35.880,1:03:41.480
Siku moja, nilikuwa kwenye gari, nilikuwa natafakari Neno la Mungu.

1:03:41.480,1:03:46.980
Nilikuwa mbele ya gari katikati ya watu wawili; dereva na mwingine mmoja.

1:03:46.980,1:03:51.520
Wakati natafakari Neno la Mungu, dereva akapiga kelele, "Hey!"

1:03:51.520,1:03:53.440
Halafu nikasema, "Yesu!"

1:03:53.440,1:03:56.820
Halafu nikajikuta niko nje, nimesimama.

1:03:56.820,1:04:04.660
Sijui jinsi nilivyofika pale - nilikuwa nimesimama nje, wakati watu wengine wamevunjika mifupa.

1:04:04.660,1:04:08.100
Walikaa kwenye gari, hawakuweza kutoka, gari lilipinduka kuviringika mara 3.

1:04:08.100,1:04:14.020
Namshukuru Mungu nilipiga kelele "Yesu!" kabla haijatokea - na nilikuwa nimesimama nje.

1:04:14.020,1:04:19.760
Lakini watu wetu siku hizi wanapiga kelele "Yesu" baada ya kutokea.

1:04:19.760,1:04:26.660
Sasa najua.

1:04:26.660,1:04:36.680
Unapiga kelele "Yesu" baada ya kupatwa na jinamizi, matatizo.

1:04:36.680,1:04:37.860
Nataka kuondoka.

1:04:37.860,1:04:42.120
Kwa mara nyingine tena- tafadhali, mjazwe.

1:04:42.120,1:04:50.180
Huduma ya SCOAN ya Jumapili

1:04:50.180,1:04:54.640
Nahitaji kupata ripoti; nitumie barua pepe na nitafuatilia.

1:04:54.640,1:04:57.520
- Haleluya!
- Amina.

1:04:57.520,1:05:07.320
Hii Biblia mnayobeba bila Roho Mtakatifu ni fasihi.

1:05:07.320,1:05:13.280
Hii Biblia mnayobeba bila Roho Mtakatifu ni historia.

1:05:13.280,1:05:23.660
Haiwezekani kwa ye yote kutii Neno la Mungu bila Roho Mtakatifu.

1:05:23.660,1:05:27.880
Sio kwamba hutatii wakati unasema, "usiseme uongo".

1:05:27.880,1:05:36.720
Bila Roho Mtakatifu unasema, "sitasema uongo tena. TB Joshua alisema kwenye ujumbe wake tusiseme uongo".

1:05:36.720,1:05:42.500
Utaweza kwa siku moja, siku mbili, siku tatu, siku nne;

1:05:42.500,1:05:47.860
Siku ya tano utakuwa muongo mkubwa.

1:05:47.860,1:05:51.100
Utalipuka.

1:05:51.100,1:05:53.400
hapo ndipo unaweza kufikia.

1:05:53.400,1:05:57.720
Lakini kwa Mungu yote yanawezekana.

1:05:57.720,1:06:04.500
lakini unaweza kufika wapi; unabaki kusema "usiseme uongo" -

1:06:04.500,1:06:07.100
Siku ya kwanza utakuwa makini;

1:06:07.100,1:06:12.620
unataka kudanganya lakini unakumbuka, "Biblia inasema tusiseme uongo".

1:06:12.620,1:06:15.020
Siku ya pili...

1:06:15.020,1:06:17.120
Siku ya tatu...

1:06:17.120,1:06:20.500
vipi wewe, mlevi?

1:06:20.500,1:06:26.060
Unaacha leo, unaacha kwa siku tano...

1:06:26.060,1:06:32.340
Kwenye ndoto wanakunywesha; utamaliza chupa 10 za bia.

1:06:32.340,1:06:37.480
Baada ya kuwa umekunywa nyingi za kutosha katika ndoto, utaamka.

1:06:37.480,1:06:43.120
Unaenda kwenye klabu ya pombe kunywa.

1:06:43.120,1:06:50.080
bila Roho Mtakatifu, hakuna wa kutii Neno la Mungu.

1:06:50.080,1:06:51.400
Mwambie jirani yako.

